WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.310
Good morning family. How are y'all doing

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:05.070
today? I'm excited to be with you. I have

00:00:05.080 --> 00:00:06.430
some things on my heart to talk to

00:00:06.430 --> 00:00:06.440
you

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:09.509
about. I went to a church

00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:13.870
service last night and it was

00:00:13.870 --> 00:00:13.880
amazing—exactly

00:00:13.880 --> 00:00:16.630
what I'm looking for. The

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:20.710
Spirit of the Lord moved, and

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:22.670
the presence of the Lord was so

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:25.470
amazing. The atmosphere

00:00:25.480 --> 00:00:29.990
was charged with His glory. I

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:31.230
just want to tell you about it a little

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:33.270
bit. My son went and he got a

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:34.830
touch from the Lord. My wife—we all were

00:00:34.840 --> 00:00:36.750
blessed. We were blessed

00:00:36.760 --> 00:00:38.229
by this church service. It's

00:00:38.239 --> 00:00:40.670
nice to just go in there and

00:00:40.680 --> 00:00:42.990
get to drink,

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:46.709
get refreshed. It was

00:00:46.719 --> 00:00:48.750
just awesome. I know there's

00:00:48.760 --> 00:00:50.910
many more to come.

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.470
Collinsville, Oklahoma is the

00:00:53.470 --> 00:00:53.480
Hiding

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:55.790
Place; I'm telling y'all,

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:57.950
Jesus is doing something huge at

00:00:57.960 --> 00:01:00.509
Collinsville, Oklahoma. I'm

00:01:00.509 --> 00:01:00.519
just human.

00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:04.030
Like I said, I'm

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:05.830
just real with you.

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:11.149
I've got issues and

00:01:11.159 --> 00:01:12.830
I work through them. We work out

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:15.030
our salvation with fear and trembling. I

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:18.190
try every single day to walk the best

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:21.190
I can. I'm hungry

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:23.310
and thirsty just like everybody else.

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:24.990
I sit in the back and I just want to

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.749
be a sponge. I sit in the

00:01:27.759 --> 00:01:29.990
very back row a lot of times and I just

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.830
watch and see if I see any angelics or

00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:35.590
angelic visitations.

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:36.789
I don't go to the front; a

00:01:36.799 --> 00:01:38.990
lot of times I like to see if

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.190
there's ministering spirits coming in

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.230
to bless the congregation, because that's

00:01:43.240 --> 00:01:46.270
what happens a lot. In this

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:48.630
case, I was just worshiping because the

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:51.069
worship was phenomenal. The glory of

00:01:51.079 --> 00:01:54.630
the Lord came in with the worship.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:56.069
I was sitting in the back, like I said,

00:01:56.079 --> 00:01:57.870
and I had my head down and all of a

00:01:57.880 --> 00:02:00.109
sudden Jesus appeared to me in

00:02:00.109 --> 00:02:00.119
an open-eyed

00:02:00.119 --> 00:02:03.029
vision. He

00:02:03.029 --> 00:02:03.039
came

00:02:03.039 --> 00:02:05.389
to me and he

00:02:05.399 --> 00:02:08.550
was this close—this close to me.

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.910
He was just observing me, but

00:02:10.920 --> 00:02:13.070
he was smiling; he had a huge smile on

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:15.270
his face, like he was laughing, and he was

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:17.790
just enjoying the service. He was

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:19.949
looking down at me.

00:02:19.959 --> 00:02:22.670
He never spoke, but

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:25.790
all of a sudden I was in

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:27.509
the Spirit. I

00:02:27.509 --> 00:02:27.519
looked

00:02:27.519 --> 00:02:30.190
down and I saw

00:02:30.190 --> 00:02:30.200
a crown—a

00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:35.990
beautiful crown full of rubies.

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:40.869
It had diamonds all

00:02:40.879 --> 00:02:44.309
around this onyx-looking stone.

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:46.309
My first initial thought was,

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:49.110
'Wow, onyx is dark. It's a black

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:52.149
stone. That's kind of

00:02:52.159 --> 00:02:54.509
evil.'But

00:02:54.519 --> 00:02:56.630
the Lord heard my

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:58.390
thoughts and He spoke to me. He

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:02.270
said, 'Brandon, I created all colors.

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:04.589
I created everything richly for you to

00:03:04.599 --> 00:03:07.869
enjoy, son. Black onyx—I made that

00:03:07.879 --> 00:03:10.630
stone; it's here from

00:03:10.630 --> 00:03:10.640
Me.'I

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:12.670
was blessed by

00:03:12.680 --> 00:03:15.509
what He said because it changed my

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:18.630
opinion about black onyx stone.

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:20.270
I was looking at

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:21.789
this

00:03:21.799 --> 00:03:24.470
crown, but standing in front of the

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:27.589
King of Kings, my heart instantaneously

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:30.110
was like, 'Oh, I want to give You something.

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:32.350
I want to honor You with

00:03:32.350 --> 00:03:32.360
something.'I

00:03:32.360 --> 00:03:34.270
looked down and I didn't have anything

00:03:34.280 --> 00:03:36.830
on me other than just me.

00:03:36.840 --> 00:03:38.589
I thought

00:03:38.589 --> 00:03:38.599
I'd

00:03:38.599 --> 00:03:40.190
just give Him me, but I was like, 'I want to

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:42.149
give more'because I'm standing in front

00:03:42.159 --> 00:03:45.229
of the King of Kings. In the vision, I

00:03:45.229 --> 00:03:45.239
picked

00:03:45.239 --> 00:03:48.350
up that beautiful crown. It had

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.830
diamonds wrapped

00:03:49.840 --> 00:03:52.149
around each one of those onyx stones, and

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:54.030
there were humongous diamonds all on

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:55.710
this. He said, 'This is your personal

00:03:55.720 --> 00:03:58.589
crown. Every one of my children

00:03:58.599 --> 00:04:00.910
will have a crown—your

00:04:00.910 --> 00:04:00.920
personal crown—when

00:04:00.920 --> 00:04:02.949
they come to heaven.'It was

00:04:02.959 --> 00:04:05.789
beautiful; there were all

00:04:05.799 --> 00:04:07.869
kinds of cool things in that

00:04:07.879 --> 00:04:11.149
crown. He told me

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:16.069
He had a crown that's designed for

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:19.949
each individual believer; it's made

00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:22.950
special for them with the jewels, and

00:04:22.960 --> 00:04:26.430
everything represents something. I

00:04:26.440 --> 00:04:29.390
picked up that crown and all I

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:31.550
could do was worship Him

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:34.790
with it by giving it to Him. I took

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:37.150
that crown in the Spirit and I handed it

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:38.950
over to Him. I was just like, 'I just

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:40.629
want to give You an offering. I just want

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:43.590
to give You something

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.990
special.'When

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.909
you're entering into the

00:04:46.919 --> 00:04:49.110
presence of a king, I wanted to bring Him

00:04:49.120 --> 00:04:51.070
a gift like the wise men brought Him

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:53.790
gold, myrrh, and frankincense. They

00:04:53.800 --> 00:04:55.510
brought Him the gifts because they were

00:04:55.520 --> 00:04:57.670
worshiping Him with them. I

00:04:57.680 --> 00:05:00.230
thought it was so beautiful. I was casting down

00:05:00.230 --> 00:05:00.240
the golden crowns

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:02.189
there. I picked it up in

00:05:02.199 --> 00:05:04.150
the Spirit, in

00:05:04.150 --> 00:05:04.160
the open-eyed

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.710
vision, and I handed it to Him.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.790
That scripture,

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:11.590
'casting down the golden

00:05:11.590 --> 00:05:11.600
crowns'—I

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:13.310
didn't have the whole scripture of it,

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:15.469
but I know it's in Revelation, I believe.

00:05:15.469 --> 00:05:15.479
It

00:05:15.479 --> 00:05:18.629
just echoed inside of

00:05:18.639 --> 00:05:21.430
me, and I blessed Him with

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:23.430
it. All He did was just smile with

00:05:23.440 --> 00:05:24.950
this love on His face. It was

00:05:24.950 --> 00:05:24.960
such

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:27.870
an honor.

00:05:27.880 --> 00:05:29.950
He received from me, but I

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:32.110
was like, 'I have nothing of my own to

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:34.510
give You, Lord, other than just me.'But I

00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:36.670
gave Him a gift out of something

00:05:36.680 --> 00:05:38.710
that He blessed me with.

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:48.270
Then He spoke to me and said, 'Brandon,

00:05:48.280 --> 00:05:50.510
I'm bringing a refreshing to my people.

00:05:50.520 --> 00:05:53.710
They're thirsty.'There's many of you

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:56.189
watching this video today that

00:05:56.199 --> 00:05:59.309
are thirsty for a fresh drink of that

00:05:59.319 --> 00:06:02.629
living water. At this moment, waves of His

00:06:02.629 --> 00:06:02.639
glory in that vision—whenever

00:06:02.639 --> 00:06:05.629
I looked over

00:06:05.639 --> 00:06:08.830
and across the front of the church—there

00:06:08.830 --> 00:06:08.840
were

00:06:08.840 --> 00:06:13.350
waves of His glory, waves

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:16.550
of His presence rolling in. I could

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:20.270
see a beautiful pink, like

00:06:20.270 --> 00:06:20.280
a

00:06:20.280 --> 00:06:24.270
sunset, with all kinds of beautiful pink

00:06:24.280 --> 00:06:26.990
colors. The waves, when they were

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:29.870
coming in, looked like they were glowing

00:06:29.880 --> 00:06:33.589
with this pink sunset color.

00:06:33.599 --> 00:06:35.870
They were coming over the people

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:37.830
and bringing a refreshing.

00:06:37.840 --> 00:06:40.870
The Lord said, 'I'm going to bring a

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:44.110
refreshing over my remnant, over my

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:46.230
people that are seeking Me.'I could

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:48.950
see the waves coming in, and He said, 'As

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:51.230
that wave comes in, I'm going to bring

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:53.309
another one right on the heels

00:06:53.309 --> 00:06:53.319
of it.'In

00:06:53.319 --> 00:06:56.150
these last days, if you stay close to

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:59.150
the vine, if you

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:03.070
abide in Me and My words remain in you, a

00:07:03.070 --> 00:07:03.080
continual refreshing...

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:05.550
you shall ask what you will and it shall

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:09.350
be done. He said, 'I'm bringing a wave

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:13.390
of my glory upon my people—a wave of

00:07:13.400 --> 00:07:17.749
refreshing, a continual

00:07:17.749 --> 00:07:17.759
refreshing—by

00:07:17.759 --> 00:07:21.070
drinking from that cup.'When I talk

00:07:21.080 --> 00:07:25.390
about 'Fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up, Lord,

00:07:25.400 --> 00:07:27.830
come and quench,'that's what I'm talking

00:07:27.830 --> 00:07:27.840
about—drinking

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:30.430
from

00:07:30.440 --> 00:07:33.110
that river of living

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:35.510
water. He said out of your belly

00:07:35.520 --> 00:07:38.909
shall flow rivers of living water.

00:07:38.919 --> 00:07:41.510
I'm telling you, there's a river of

00:07:41.520 --> 00:07:44.270
living water that's going to start to

00:07:44.280 --> 00:07:46.110
bubble out

00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:49.469
of you as you stay close to Him and you

00:07:49.479 --> 00:07:52.110
seek Him daily. He's going to bring a

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:54.589
refreshing over you. So I'm going to

00:07:54.599 --> 00:07:57.950
believe God with you today for a fresh

00:07:57.960 --> 00:08:03.149
drink of that water. Jesus wants to become real to those in a

00:08:03.159 --> 00:08:06.589
place of desperation—those

00:08:06.589 --> 00:08:06.599
who are

00:08:06.599 --> 00:08:09.510
so hungry and

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:12.469
thirsty and desperate for Him

00:08:12.479 --> 00:08:15.070
to touch you in a mighty way. I'm

00:08:15.080 --> 00:08:19.149
telling you, Jesus wants to become real

00:08:19.159 --> 00:08:22.430
to you and become that fresh

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:25.029
drink for you so that you're not dry and

00:08:25.039 --> 00:08:27.270
you're not burned out. There's a

00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:28.909
lot of you that are wanting to give up

00:08:28.919 --> 00:08:31.029
on things—wanting to give up on ministry,

00:08:31.039 --> 00:08:32.469
your marriage,

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:33.829
your children,

00:08:33.839 --> 00:08:35.870
your jobs,

00:08:35.870 --> 00:08:35.880
whatever—saying,

00:08:35.880 --> 00:08:37.949
'I can't take the

00:08:37.959 --> 00:08:40.709
pressure anymore; this has become too

00:08:40.719 --> 00:08:43.190
hard to keep going

00:08:43.190 --> 00:08:43.200
through.'The

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:45.070
Lord wants to give you a fresh touch

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.310
today. He told me, 'Brandon, I want

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:49.630
to give my people a

00:08:49.630 --> 00:08:49.640
drink.'There's

00:08:49.640 --> 00:08:51.230
a lot of you

00:08:51.230 --> 00:08:51.240
in

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:53.710
that desperation of saying, 'Hey, I've

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:55.630
been battling this sickness,

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:57.710
this disease,

00:08:57.720 --> 00:09:00.470
this depression, anxiety, or fear. How can I

00:09:00.470 --> 00:09:00.480
get through this?

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:02.949
I can't go

00:09:02.949 --> 00:09:02.959
anymore.'You

00:09:02.959 --> 00:09:05.269
keep rehearsing it: 'God, where are You? How

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:07.509
can I get through this?'But I'm telling

00:09:07.519 --> 00:09:10.430
you, the Lord told me last night,

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.430
'I want to bring a fresh touch on my

00:09:12.430 --> 00:09:12.440
people,'and

00:09:12.440 --> 00:09:15.310
He wants to bring it now.

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:17.230
I was sitting there,

00:09:17.240 --> 00:09:20.470
and like I said, I deal with my own

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:23.030
things. I was believing maybe

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:25.550
next service I'll get my

00:09:25.560 --> 00:09:27.670
breakthrough for what I'm believing

00:09:27.670 --> 00:09:27.680
for—for

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:30.630
my daughter, Megan. Maybe

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:33.910
next time I'm in church, maybe Megan will

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:36.470
get her full manifestation. Maybe I'll

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.470
get my full manifestation of things that

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:41.030
I'm believing for. The Lord stopped

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:42.870
me in that same vision, in that same

00:09:42.880 --> 00:09:44.670
experience, and said,

00:09:44.680 --> 00:09:46.509
'Brandon, why not

00:09:46.519 --> 00:09:50.389
now? Why do you always push off the

00:09:50.399 --> 00:09:53.150
miracle for tomorrow when I'm ready to

00:09:53.160 --> 00:09:56.990
do it now?'Faith calls those things that

00:09:57.000 --> 00:10:00.630
be not as though they are—right now. Why do I always

00:10:00.630 --> 00:10:00.640
push off the miracle?

00:10:00.640 --> 00:10:03.670
Faith calls it now.

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:04.990
The Lord's not always telling you

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:06.790
it's tomorrow—that in the 'sweet by

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:08.150
and by'you're going to get it.

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:14.790
Receive it now. Abraham staggered not

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:17.230
at the promise of God through unbelief,

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:19.750
but he was strong in faith, believing and

00:10:19.760 --> 00:10:23.430
fully persuaded that what God had

00:10:23.430 --> 00:10:23.440
promised,

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:27.269
He was able also to perform it.

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:29.389
I want you to believe right now in

00:10:29.399 --> 00:10:32.389
your circumstances for your

00:10:32.389 --> 00:10:32.399
'now.'Now

00:10:32.399 --> 00:10:35.670
faith is the substance of

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:37.350
things hoped for and evidence of things

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:40.230
not seen. 'Now'is the things you're

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:42.829
believing for—not tomorrow, not next

00:10:42.839 --> 00:10:45.910
service, not when you get around

00:10:45.920 --> 00:10:48.389
another healing minister.

00:10:48.399 --> 00:10:50.990
Believe for your

00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:53.750
manifestation today.

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:55.790
I'm always having

00:10:55.800 --> 00:10:58.550
thoughts like, 'Maybe next time,

00:10:58.560 --> 00:11:01.430
maybe a year from now, maybe

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:03.829
my breakthrough will

00:11:06.790 --> 00:11:06.800
come.'You're

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:12.750
always

00:11:12.760 --> 00:11:14.590
kicking that can down the road that

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:16.670
God's going to do something. But we're

00:11:16.680 --> 00:11:20.990
going to believe God for today for your

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:23.910
miracle. We're going to believe God today

00:11:23.920 --> 00:11:27.030
for your fresh touch—for a drink that

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:28.990
will fill your cup because

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.949
you're lifting it up and quench

00:11:30.959 --> 00:11:33.870
the thirsting of your soul. I believe

00:11:33.880 --> 00:11:37.030
with all my heart Jesus is the restorer of

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:39.629
all things, that nothing is

00:11:39.639 --> 00:11:42.790
impossible for Him. Whatever you put

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:46.069
your hands to will prosper. Whatever

00:11:46.079 --> 00:11:48.590
you touch will be blessed because

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:51.269
you're a child of the King. Greater

00:11:51.279 --> 00:11:53.670
is He that is in you than he that is in

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:56.310
the world. A thousand shall

00:11:56.320 --> 00:11:58.870
fall at your side and ten thousand at your

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:01.030
right hand, but nothing shall come

00:12:01.030 --> 00:12:01.040
nigh.

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:05.389
I believe with all my heart Jesus

00:12:05.399 --> 00:12:07.790
paid the price for you to walk in

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:10.269
victory from sickness and disease, from

00:12:10.279 --> 00:12:13.350
bondage, from addictions. It doesn't

00:12:13.360 --> 00:12:16.150
